江永康市一家工貿公司在網上貼文：「為慶祝日本大地震，即日起三天內，一律超低價拍賣。餘震不斷，活動不止，如果震八級，價格更低。若死十萬，價格更爛，若日沈底，清倉處理。」<br />\n<br />\n雲南昆明一家物防門控公司在官方微博發帖稱：「為慶祝日本大地震，在本公司所有產品，一律超低價，餘震不斷，活動不變，如震9級，價格還低，日若死完，價格爛賤，若日沈底，我們的產品全部歸你。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/voa-news-chinese-nationalists-hail-kumamoto-earthquake-20160418/3290221.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fvoa-news-chinese-nationalists-hail-kumamoto-earthquake-20160418%2F3290221.html&d=phjnG9xxvo1UK5UCce3J09tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fcbc9ca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/voa-news-chinese-nationalists-hail-kumamoto-earthquake-20160418/3290221.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定又係插贓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13222fb853f64b69c0c0c7456fba4a1637e46fa5","tid":394180,"uid":97240,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來冇人話過係大陸學生做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜支那唔係好想香港人寫殘體字㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家香港人跟足大陸咁做又唔啱聽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有親中既人既智商都低過99<br />\n除左高層果批"},{"pid":"3a4d7fbf5af57ef0acab7c664797d4d1c35ab7ec","tid":394180,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":63,"score":-63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:43:16.000Z","msg":"所以話盲反大陸d人特別係後生仔真係冇腦又衝動<br />\n你要做就做到足啦<br />\n明明憎一個人應該好了解對方先岩<br />\n但而家敵人一睇就知你係咩質素既對手<br />\n影衰自己"},{"pid":"3cb88b22175fb551641937db4889deec976ea4f6","tid":394180,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"唔係特登俾佢試反應嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一睇就知唔似啦"},{"pid":"b7201007a191f574996a5b070b691278c20dc432","tid":394180,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"現代版慰安婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png